name: Lollababy bottle warmer (V2.0)
description:
Warm liquids quickly with the Lollababy Bottle Warmer! For the parent on the go. Compatible with most wide-neck baby bottle brands, our bottle warmer is perfect for any situation outside the family home. It is also beautifully designed with a modern digital display for easy temperature selection and reading. Other features:

• Night Light. Better visibility during night feeds.
• Quick Heating. 10 minutes or less.
• Multiple Temperature Settings. 37°, 40°, 45°, 50°.
• Heat Retention. Up to 12 hours; liquid stays at chosen temperature until warmer is removed.

Compatible Wide-Neck Baby Bottle Brand List:
1. AVENT
2. Richell
3. Combi
4. SpeCtra
5. Nip
6. Chicco

*Note: Glass bottles are not compatible with this bottle warmer without adaptor.

• Adaptors Available. Multiple bottle adaptors available for purchase under accessories.

• Easy to wash.

Dimensions & Weight: 76 x 76 x 96mm / 400G

Safety Features:

Automatic Power Off
Dry Heating Protection
Overheating Fuse Protection
Battery Overcharge Protection
Technical Specs:

SUS316 Stainless Steel
4400mAh Li-ion Battery
Charging Time – 2A-6h, 3A-4h
2-6 warming times per full charge.
Bottle Warmer Kit contains:

• 1 Bottle Warmer Unit
• 1 Dust Cover
• 1 USB Cable
• 1 Sealing Ring
